object.script: function onTick() C = input.getBool(1) G = input.getBool(2) D = input.getBool(3) end function onDraw() screen.setColor(30, 30, 30) screen.drawRectF(-25, 26, 32, 7) screen.setColor(30, 30, 30,110) screen.drawRectF(-24, 24, 32, 7) if C == false and G then screen.setColor(0, 250, 0) screen.drawLine(0, 10, 6, 10) end if C then screen.setColor(0, 0, 250) screen.drawLine(0, 10, 6, 10) end if D and C == false then screen.setColor(250, 0, 0) screen.drawLine(0, 10, 6, 10) end end

function onTick() S = input.getNumber(1) R = input.getNumber(2) G = (S*R)/3.5 R = input.getBool(4) end function onDraw() screen.setColor(30, 30, 30) screen.drawRectF(25, 26, 32, 7) screen.setColor(30, 30, 30,110) screen.drawRectF(24, 24, 32, 7) if S > 65 and S < 85 then screen.setColor(250, 250, b) screen.drawLine(27, 10, 33, 10) else screen.setColor(30, 30, 10) screen.drawLine(27, 10, 33, 10) end if S > 50 and S < 70 then screen.setColor(0, 250, b) screen.drawLine(27, 11, 33, 11) else screen.setColor(10, 30, 10) screen.drawLine(27, 11, 33, 11) end if S > 25 and S < 55 then screen.setColor(250, 0, b) screen.drawLine(27, 12, 33, 12) else screen.setColor(30, 10, 10) screen.drawLine(27, 12, 33, 12) end screen.setColor(250, 250, 250) screen.drawText(28, 2, string.format("%.0fG",G)) if R then screen.setColor(250, 0, 0) screen.drawRectF(27, 27, 2, 2) end end

object.script:
function onTick() if not initialized then marginLR=property.getNumber("margin") direction=property.getBool("alignment") and -1 or 1 hEnabled=property.getBool("heading indicator") bandColor=tonumber(property.getText("band color"),16) b=bandColor & 0xff g=(bandColor>>8) & 0xff r=(bandColor>>16) & 0xff targetColor=tonumber(property.getText("target color"),16) tb=targetColor & 0xff tg=(targetColor>>8) & 0xff tr=(targetColor>>16) & 0xff initialized=true end heading=((1-input.getNumber(1))%1)*360 tBearing=input.getNumber(2) tEnabled=input.getBool(1) end
function onDraw() w=screen.getWidth() cx=w/2 h=70 dx=math.ceil(math.max(2,math.min(w/30,5))) if direction>0 then borderY=0 textY=3 else borderY=h-1 textY=h-8 end
screen.setColor(r,g,b,100) ang0=heading//5*5 angle=ang0 x0=math.floor(cx-(heading-ang0)*dx/5+.5) x=x0 repeat DrawTick(x,angle) angle=angle+5 x=x+dx until x>=w-marginLR angle=ang0 x=x0-dx repeat angle=angle-5 DrawTick(x,angle) x=x-dx until x<marginLR
screen.setColor(r,g,b) screen.drawLine(cx,borderY,cx,borderY+direction*2) if hEnabled then number=string.format("%1.0f",heading) screen.drawText((w-number:len()*5)/2+1,textY,number) end
if tEnabled then screen.setColor(tr,tg,tb) relBearing=(heading-tBearing)%360 if relBearing>180 then relBearing=relBearing-360 end x=math.max(marginLR,math.min(cx-(relBearing*dx/5), w-marginLR-1)) screen.drawLine(x,borderY,x,borderY+direction*2) screen.drawLine(x-1,borderY,x+2,borderY) end screen.setColor(0, 0, 0) screen.drawRectF(0, 60, 35, 96) screen.drawRectF(61, 60, 35, 96) end
function DrawTick(x,ang) ang=ang%360 if ang%15==0 then screen.drawLine(x,borderY,x,borderY+direction*2) if hEnabled==false or x<w/2-12 or x>w/2+12 then if ang==0 then screen.drawText(x-1,textY,"N") elseif ang==45 then screen.drawText(x-4,textY,"NE") elseif ang==90 then screen.drawText(x-1,textY,"E") elseif ang==135 then screen.drawText(x-4,textY,"SE") elseif ang==180 then screen.drawText(x-1,textY,"S") elseif ang==225 then screen.drawText(x-4,textY,"SW") elseif ang==270 then screen.drawText(x-1,textY,"W") elseif ang==315 then screen.drawText(x-4,textY,"NW") end end else screen.drawLine(x,borderY,x,borderY+direction) end end

PD = 0 P = 0 line = screen.drawLine cos = math.cos sin = math.sin rad = math.rad COL = screen.setColor WM = property.getBool("whisky marker") BG = property.getBool("background") LiD = math.ceil(property.getNumber("line degree")) Vline = property.getBool("vertical line") function onTick() P = input.getNumber(1)*360 R = input.getNumber(2)*360 V = input.getNumber(3)
R2 = R-90 R3 = R+90 if V < 0 then P = P*-1 R = R R2 = R2*-1 else P = P*-1 R = R*-1 R2 = R2 end RD = rad(R) RD2 = rad(R2) LD = 16 SLD = 12 RC = cos(RD) RS = sin(RD) RC2 = cos(RD2) RC3 = cos(rad(R3)) RS2 = sin(RD2) PRS = P*RS2 PRC = P*RC2 MCP = math.ceil(P) end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = 96 w2 = w/2 h2 = h/2 COL(0,0,255,0) if WM then line(w2,h2,w2-4,h2+3) line(w2-4,h2+3,w2-8,h2) line(w2-8,h2,w2-26,h2) line(w2,h2,w2+4,h2+3) line(w2+4,h2+3,w2+8,h2) line(w2+8,h2,w2+26,h2) end COL(0,255,0,200) line(w2-PRC+5*RC,h2-PRS-5*RS,w2-PRC+LD*RC,h2-PRS-LD*RS) line(w2-PRC-LD*RC,h2-PRS+LD*RS,w2-PRC-5*RC,h2-PRS+5*RS) line(w2-PRC-LD*RC,h2-PRS+LD*RS,(w2-PRC-LD*RC)+5*RC2,(h2-PRS+LD*RS)+5*RS2) line(w2-PRC+LD*RC,h2-PRS-LD*RS,(w2-PRC+LD*RC)+5*RC2,(h2-PRS-LD*RS)+5*RS2)
for PD = -LiD,-90,-LiD do if PD+MCP < 25 and PD+P > -25 then COL(0,255,0,250) line((w2-PD*RC2)-PRC-7*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS+7*RS,(w2-PD*RC2)-PRC-SLD*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS+SLD*RS) line((w2-PD*RC2)-PRC+SLD*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS-SLD*RS,(w2-PD*RC2)-PRC+7*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS-7*RS) line((w2-PD*RC2)-PRC-SLD*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS+SLD*RS,(w2-PD*RC2)-PRC-SLD*RC+5*RC2,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS+SLD*RS+5*RS2) line((w2-PD*RC2)-PRC+SLD*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS-SLD*RS,(w2-PD*RC2)-PRC+SLD*RC+5*RC2,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS-SLD*RS+5*RS2) COL(0,255,0,200) screen.drawText((w2-PD*RC2)-PRC-4*RC,(h2-3-PD*RS2)-PRS,math.abs(PD)) end end for PD = LiD,90,LiD do if PD+MCP < 25 and PD+P > -25 then COL(0,250,0,250) line((w2-PD*RC2)-PRC-7*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS+7*RS,(w2-PD*RC2)-PRC-SLD*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS+SLD*RS) line((w2-PD*RC2)-PRC+SLD*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS-SLD*RS,(w2-PD*RC2)-PRC+7*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS-7*RS) line((w2-PD*RC2)-PRC-SLD*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS+SLD*RS,(w2-PD*RC2)-PRC-SLD*RC+5*RC2,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS+SLD*RS+5*RS2) line((w2-PD*RC2)-PRC+SLD*RC,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS-SLD*RS,(w2-PD*RC2)-PRC+SLD*RC+5*RC2,(h2-PD*RS2)-PRS-SLD*RS+5*RS2) COL(0,255,0,200) screen.drawText((w2-PD*RC2)-PRC-4*RC,(h2-3-PD*RS2)-PRS,PD) end end screen.setColor(0, 0, 0) screen.drawRectF(0, 60, 96, 96) end

function onTick() C = input.getNumber(2) R1 = input.getNumber(3) M = input.getNumber(7) H = (input.getNumber(4)*400)+16 HB = (H/2)+8 V = (input.getNumber(5)*-400)+16 ALT = input.getNumber(6)/100 THR = input.getNumber(8) * 10 B = (input.getNumber(10)/29.41)+3 W = input.getBool(1) C = input.getBool(3) end
function onDraw() screen.setColor(30, 30, 30) screen.drawRectF(0, 26, 32, 7) screen.setColor(30, 30, 30,110) screen.drawRectF(0, 24, 32, 7) if M == 1 then screen.setColor(r, 200, b) screen.drawCircle(3, 29, 1) else screen.setColor(10, 20, 10) screen.drawCircle(3, 29, 1) end if M == 2 then screen.setColor(r, 200, b) screen.drawCircle(8, 29, 1) else screen.setColor(10, 20, 10) screen.drawCircle(8, 29, 1) end if M == 3 then screen.setColor(r, 200, b) screen.drawCircle(13, 29, 1) else screen.setColor(10, 20, 10) screen.drawCircle(13, 29, 1) end if M == 0 then screen.setColor(r, 200, b) screen.drawCircle(18, 29, 1) else screen.setColor(10, 20, 10) screen.drawCircle(18, 29, 1) end if W then screen.setColor(255, 255, 0) screen.drawRectF(25, 28, 7, 5) else screen.setColor(20, 20, 0) screen.drawRectF(25, 28, 7, 5) end if C and M == 0 then screen.drawLine(14, 2, 18, 2) end end

function onTick() IAS = input.getNumber(1) ALT = input.getNumber(2) RNG = input.getNumber(3) CRP = 100-(input.getNumber(10)/10) h = (input.getNumber(4)*1200)+48 v = (input.getNumber(5)*-1200)+48 t = input.getNumber(6) M = input.getNumber(7) Thr = input.getNumber(8)*10 i1 = input.getNumber(9) e = input.getNumber(11)+100 T = input.getBool(1) w = input.getBool(2) end function onDraw() screen.setColor(r, 255, b) screen.drawText(0, 30, string.format("%.0f",IAS)) screen.drawTextBox(66, 30,30, 5, string.format("%.0f",ALT),1,0) if T and M == 0 then screen.drawText(24, 50, "NAVIGATION") end if T and M == 1 then screen.drawText(20, 50, "LASER GUIDED") end if T and M == 2 then screen.drawText(26, 50, "CCRP BOMB") end if T and M == 3 then screen.drawText(40, 50, "A-A") end if Thr < 9 then screen.drawText(0, 38, string.format("%.0f",Thr)) else screen.drawText(0, 38, "F") end if i1 > 9.99 then screen.drawText(70, 60, string.format("%.2f",i1)) else screen.drawText(75, 60, string.format("%.2f",i1)) end if RNG > 100 then screen.drawTextBox(66, 53,30,5 ,string.format("%.0f",RNG),1,0) else screen.drawText(80, 53, "000") end if M == 1 or M == 2 then screen.drawTextBox(65, 68,30,5 ,string.format("%.0f",e),1,0) screen.setColor(0, 0, 0) screen.drawRectF(82, 68, 4, 5) screen.setColor(r, 255, b) screen.drawText(83, 68, ":") end if M == 1 then screen.drawText(0, 63, "L36A") screen.drawCircle(h, v, 5) end if M == 2 then screen.drawText(0, 63, "GBU10") screen.drawLine(h, 0, h, 60) screen.drawCircle(h, 60, 5) screen.drawRect(h-1,CRP+5, 3, 3) end if M == 3 then screen.drawText(0, 63, "R80E") end if M == 3 and RNG > 100 then screen.drawCircle(h, v, 5) end if M == 3 and RNG < 100 then screen.drawCircle(48, 35, 25) end
end

function onTick() if not initialized then marginLR=property.getNumber("margin") direction=property.getBool("alignment") and -1 or 1 hEnabled=property.getBool("heading indicator") bandColor=tonumber(property.getText("band color"),16) b=bandColor & 0xff g=(bandColor>>8) & 0xff r=(bandColor>>16) & 0xff targetColor=tonumber(property.getText("target color"),16) tb=targetColor & 0xff tg=(targetColor>>8) & 0xff tr=(targetColor>>16) & 0xff initialized=true end heading=((1-input.getNumber(1))%1)*360 tBearing=input.getNumber(2) tEnabled=input.getBool(1) end
function onDraw() w=screen.getWidth() cx=w/2 h=70 dx=math.ceil(math.max(2,math.min(w/30,5))) if direction>0 then borderY=0 textY=3 else borderY=h-1 textY=h-8 end
screen.setColor(r,g,b,100) ang0=heading//5*5 angle=ang0 x0=math.floor(cx-(heading-ang0)*dx/5+.5) x=x0 repeat DrawTick(x,angle) angle=angle+5 x=x+dx until x>=w-marginLR angle=ang0 x=x0-dx repeat angle=angle-5 DrawTick(x,angle) x=x-dx until x<marginLR
screen.setColor(r,g,b) screen.drawLine(cx,borderY,cx,borderY+direction*2) if hEnabled then number=string.format("%1.0f",heading) screen.drawText((w-number:len()*5)/2+1,textY,number) end
if tEnabled then screen.setColor(tr,tg,tb) relBearing=(heading-tBearing)%360 if relBearing>180 then relBearing=relBearing-360 end x=math.max(marginLR,math.min(cx-(relBearing*dx/5), w-marginLR-1)) screen.drawLine(x,borderY,x,borderY+direction*2) screen.drawLine(x-1,borderY,x+2,borderY) end screen.setColor(0, 0, 0) screen.drawRectF(0, 60, 35, 96) screen.drawRectF(61, 60, 35, 96) end
function DrawTick(x,ang) ang=ang%360 if ang%15==0 then screen.drawLine(x,borderY,x,borderY+direction*2) if hEnabled==false or x<w/2-12 or x>w/2+12 then if ang==0 then screen.drawText(x-1,textY,"N") elseif ang==45 then screen.drawText(x-4,textY,"NE") elseif ang==90 then screen.drawText(x-1,textY,"E") elseif ang==135 then screen.drawText(x-4,textY,"SE") elseif ang==180 then screen.drawText(x-1,textY,"S") elseif ang==225 then screen.drawText(x-4,textY,"SW") elseif ang==270 then screen.drawText(x-1,textY,"W") elseif ang==315 then screen.drawText(x-4,textY,"NW") end end else screen.drawLine(x,borderY,x,borderY+direction) end end

object.script: function onTick() X = input.getNumber(3) Y = input.getNumber(4) S = input.getBool(3) P1 = input.getBool(1) Z = input.getNumber(6) Zoom = P1 and isPointInRectangle(X, Y, 26, 0, 6, 6) NV = P1 and isPointInRectangle(X, Y, 26, 8, 6, 6) output.setBool(1, Zoom) output.setBool(2, NV) end function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end function onDraw() screen.setColor(0, 70, 0, 100) screen.drawRect(1, 1, 29, 26) screen.drawRect(2, 2, 27, 24) screen.setColor(0, 30, 0, 100) screen.drawRectF(0, 0, 32, 32) if S then screen.setColor(0, 25, 0) screen.drawRectF(0, 0, 32, 32) screen.setColor(0, 100, 0) screen.drawText(6, 3, "WARM") screen.drawText(8, 9, "TGP") screen.drawText(6, 20, "P") end screen.setColor(0, 40, 0) screen.drawLine(12, 15, 7, 15) screen.drawLine(20, 15, 25, 15) screen.drawLine(16, 19, 16, 24) if Zoom then screen.drawRectF(29, 0, 3, 5) else screen.drawRect(29, 0, 3, 5) end if NV then screen.drawRectF(29, 8, 3, 5) else screen.drawRect(29, 8, 3, 5) end if Z < 0.9 then screen.drawRect(14, 13, 4, 4) end end

object.script: function onTick() x = input.getNumber(2) y = input.getNumber(3) z = (input.getNumber(1)/400)+2 xt = input.getNumber(7) - x yt = input.getNumber(8) - y end function onDraw() screen.setColor(250, 255, 250) screen.drawMap(x, y, z) screen.setMapColorOcean(0, 10, 0) screen.setMapColorShallows(0, 20,0) screen.setMapColorLand(0, 100, 0) screen.setMapColorGrass(0, 40, 0) screen.setMapColorSand(0, 150, 0) screen.setMapColorSnow(0, 190, 0) pixelX, pixelY = map.mapToScreen(x, y, z, 32, 32, x, y) screen.drawCircle(pixelx, pixely, 1) screen.drawText(2, 2, string.format("x%.0f",z)) xr, yr = map.mapToScreen(x, y, z, 32, 32, xt, yt) screen.setColor(250, 250, 250,250) screen.drawCircleF(xr, yr, 0.7) end

function onTick()S = input.getNumber(1)W1 = 4-input.getNumber(2)W2 = 4-input.getNumber(3)W3 = 2-input.getNumber(4)end function onDraw()if S == 1 then screen.setColor(50, g, b)screen.drawRectF(2, 1, 20, 7)screen.setColor(250, g, b)screen.drawText(3, 2, "L38A")screen.drawText(25, 2, string.format("%.0f",W1))else screen.setColor(r, 50, b)screen.drawRectF(2, 1, 20, 7)screen.setColor(r, 250, b)screen.drawText(3, 2, "L38A")screen.drawText(25, 2, string.format("%.0f",W1))end if S == 2 then screen.setColor(50, g, b)screen.drawRectF(2, 10, 20, 7)screen.setColor(250, g, b)screen.drawText(3, 11, "GB10")screen.drawText(25, 11, string.format("%.0f",W2))else screen.setColor(r, 50, b)screen.drawRectF(2, 10, 20, 7)screen.setColor(r, 250, b)screen.drawText(3, 11, "GB10")screen.drawText(25, 11, string.format("%.0f",W2))end if S == 3 then screen.setColor(50, g, b)screen.drawRectF(2, 19, 20, 7)screen.setColor(250, g, b)screen.drawText(3, 20, "R80E")screen.drawText(25, 20, string.format("%.0f",W3))else screen.setColor(r, 50, b)screen.drawRectF(2, 19, 20, 7)screen.setColor(r, 250, b)screen.drawText(3, 20, "R80E")screen.drawText(25, 20, string.format("%.0f",W3))end end

function onTick() t = input.getNumber(14) t2 = input.getNumber(15) Hum = input.getNumber(6) end function onDraw() screen.setColor(r, 50, b) screen.drawRectF(0, 9, 32, 8) screen.setColor(r, 250, b) screen.drawText(32-28+t2, 2, string.format("%.2f",t)) screen.drawText(0, 10, "Visblty:") if Hum < 0.2 then screen.drawText(3, 18, "Great") end if Hum < 0.4 and Hum > 0.2 then screen.drawText(3, 18, "Good") end if Hum < 0.6 and Hum > 0.4 then screen.drawText(3, 18, "Foggy") end if Hum < 1 and Hum > 0.6 then screen.drawText(3, 18, "BAD") end end

function onTick() inputX = input.getNumber(3) inputY = input.getNumber(4) Hit = input.getBool(1) a = Hit and B1(inputX, inputY, 2, 27, 5, 4) b = Hit and B2(inputX, inputY, 8, 27, 5, 4) c = Hit and B3(inputX, inputY, 17, 27, 5, 4) d = Hit and B4(inputX, inputY, 24, 27, 5, 4) if a then output.setNumber(1, 1)end if b then output.setNumber(1, 2)end if c then output.setNumber(1, 3)end if d then output.setNumber(1, 4)end end function B1(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end function B2(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end function B3(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end function B4(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end function onDraw() screen.setColor(20, 20, 20) screen.drawRectF(0, 28, 32, 5) screen.drawRect(0, 0, 31, 31) screen.setColor(80, 80, 80) if a then screen.drawRectF(3, 28, 3, 3) else screen.drawRect(3, 28, 3, 3) end if b then screen.drawRectF(10, 28, 3, 3) else screen.drawRect(10, 28, 3, 3) end if c then screen.drawRectF(18, 28, 3, 3) else screen.drawRect(18, 28, 3, 3) end if d then screen.drawRectF(25, 28, 3, 3) else screen.drawRect(25, 28, 3, 3) end end

object.script: function onTick() X = input.getNumber(3) Y = input.getNumber(4) S = input.getBool(3) P1 = input.getBool(1) Z = input.getNumber(6) Zoom = P1 and isPointInRectangle(X, Y, 26, 0, 6, 6) NV = P1 and isPointInRectangle(X, Y, 26, 8, 6, 6) output.setBool(1, Zoom) output.setBool(2, NV) end function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end function onDraw() screen.setColor(0, 70, 0, 100) screen.drawRect(1, 1, 29, 26) screen.drawRect(2, 2, 27, 24) screen.setColor(0, 30, 0, 100) screen.drawRectF(0, 0, 32, 32) if S then screen.setColor(0, 25, 0) screen.drawRectF(0, 0, 32, 32) screen.setColor(0, 100, 0) screen.drawText(6, 3, "WARM") screen.drawText(6, 20, "A") screen.drawText(8, 9, "TGP") end screen.setColor(0, 40, 0) screen.drawLine(12, 15, 7, 15) screen.drawLine(20, 15, 25, 15) screen.drawLine(16, 19, 16, 24) if Zoom then screen.drawRectF(29, 0, 3, 5) else screen.drawRect(29, 0, 3, 5) end if NV then screen.drawRectF(29, 8, 3, 5) else screen.drawRect(29, 8, 3, 5) end if Z < 0.9 then screen.drawRect(14, 13, 4, 4) end end

function onTick() NV = input.getNumber(5) inputX = input.getNumber(3) inputY = input.getNumber(4) isPressed = input.getBool(1) Up = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 12, 2, 8, 5) Down = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 12, 24, 8, 5) Left = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 0, 12, 7, 8) Right = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 28, 12, 5, 8) FLIR = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 22, 1, 10, 8) -- Set the composite output, on/off channel 1 output.setBool(1, Up) output.setBool(2, Down) output.setBool(3, Left) output.setBool(4, Right) output.setBool(5, FLIR) end
-- Returns true if the point (x, y) is inside the rectangle at (rectX, rectY) with width rectW and height rectH function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end
function onDraw() screen.setColor(r, 250, 0,100) if Up then screen.drawRectF(12, 2, 8, 3) else screen.drawRect(12, 2, 8, 3) end if Down then screen.drawRectF(12, 24, 8, 3) else screen.drawRect(12, 24, 8, 3) end if Left then screen.drawRectF(2, 12, 3, 8) else screen.drawRect(2, 12, 3, 8) end if Right then screen.drawRectF(28, 12, 3, 8) else screen.drawRect(28, 12, 3, 8) end if NV then screen.drawTextBox(22, 1, 10, 7, "IR", 0, 0) else screen.drawTextBox(22, 1, 10, 7, "NR", 0, 0) end if 1 > 0 then screen.setColor(r, 250, 0) screen.drawRect(11, 11, 10, 10) end end

function onTick() NV = input.getNumber(5) inputX = input.getNumber(3) inputY = input.getNumber(4) isPressed = input.getBool(1) Up = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 12, 2, 8, 5) Down = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 12, 24, 8, 5) Left = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 0, 12, 7, 8) Right = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 28, 12, 5, 8) FLIR = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 22, 1, 10, 8) -- Set the composite output, on/off channel 1 output.setBool(1, Up) output.setBool(2, Down) output.setBool(3, Left) output.setBool(4, Right) output.setBool(5, FLIR) end
-- Returns true if the point (x, y) is inside the rectangle at (rectX, rectY) with width rectW and height rectH function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end
function onDraw() screen.setColor(r, 250, 0,100) if Up then screen.drawRectF(12, 2, 8, 3) else screen.drawRect(12, 2, 8, 3) end if Down then screen.drawRectF(12, 24, 8, 3) else screen.drawRect(12, 24, 8, 3) end if Left then screen.drawRectF(2, 12, 3, 8) else screen.drawRect(2, 12, 3, 8) end if Right then screen.drawRectF(28, 12, 3, 8) else screen.drawRect(28, 12, 3, 8) end if NV then screen.drawTextBox(22, 1, 10, 7, "IR", 0, 0) else screen.drawTextBox(22, 1, 10, 7, "NR", 0, 0) end if 1 > 0 then screen.setColor(r, 250, 0) screen.drawRect(11, 11, 10, 10) end end
